race.comment: MISS DE MEDICI (10) made good improvement beaten 1.7L at Gatton over 1400m. Drops back 200m for this and maps for a soft run. KWT goes aboard and will give her every chance. CEEKAY'S CHOICE (1) switched from the Gollan yard and went close this grade at Gatton off a 44-day freshen. Threatened in better than this in her two prior and if the wide gate is managed she can make the finish. ELIZABASS (3) resumed as favourite in a 62 at Kilcoy and gave a big sight from the front before being swamped late beaten 2.5L. Was galloped on at the Gold Coast following in much stronger than this. Has been given 47 days to get over that and jumps from the rail. She'd go close if she found anything like her Victorian best. DAITANNA (6) didn't finish it off at Lismore but the Maiden win prior at the Sunshine Coast suggested there was more to come. Has to go in. Include MISHANI STELLER (16) at a price.
